dc_title_s: Tripoli 1:100,000. Ez-Zauia and El-Maamura. Sheets 1373 and 1473. Series Provisional G.S.G.S. 3980
dc_description_s: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. Provisional G.S.G.S. 3980. United States. Army Map Service. Alternate title: 1:100,000 Tripoli. Sheet 1373, Ez-Zauia and Sheet 1473, El Maamura. Relief shown by 25 metres and 5 metre (approximate) contour interval and spot heights. Reproduced by Great Britain. Army. Royal Engineers. Field Survey Coy., 512 (A. Fd. Svy) Coy R. E. from Italian 1:100,000 sheet, Ez-Zauia and Sheet 1473 El Maamura, published by the Istituto Geografico Militare, 1934. Map is part of a set of 31 sheets.
